Secure Secrets
Add the following secrets to your GitHub repository:

DOCKER_USERNAME: Your Docker Hub username.
DOCKER_PASSWORD: Your Docker Hub password or access token.
KUBECONFIG: Base64-encoded Kubernetes configuration.

To generate the base64-encoded KUBECONFIG:

bash: cat ~/.kube/config | base64



Rollback Mechanism

"The kubectl rollout undo" command ensures the previous deployment state is restored if a failure is detected during rollout.
